marketing management design a strategy to build profitable customer relationship, it mainly cater to 4 things
	the production concept (available & affordable)
	the product concept (quality & performance)
	the selling concept (sales volume)
	the marketing concept (costumer's satisfaction)

marketing mix is the combination of variables that contributes to marketing success,usually its 4p, product price place and promotion

customer needs, wants, and demands
customer value, customers value product differently
